Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.57,Style1,,0,0,0,,'lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.58,Style1,,0,0,0,,Ah, {\i1}Arai- kun!{\i0}
